  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cmain\u003e\u003carticle aria-label=\"Tzatziki\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you have never had tzatziki sauce before, it’s like a savory, fresh tasting dip or spread made mostly of Greek yogurt. It’s flavorful, easy to make and packed with protein and probiotics as a big bonus to the delicious flavor it adds to a meal or appetizer. I love it!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTzatziki (pronounced tuh zee kee) is the Greek word for this dip or sauce, but it also goes by the Turkish cacik. This dish is wonderful as a dip with warm pita and sliced vegetables like bell peppers, carrots or cucumbers. I also love it as a sauce or spread on things like a \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/homemade-falafel-cucumber-dressing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003efalafel \u003c/a\u003ewrap.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRelated: \u003c/strong\u003eLooking for more great dip recipes? Next up, try \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/whipped-feta-dip/\"\u003ewhipped feta\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/smoked-salmon-dip/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003esmoked salmon dip\u003c/a\u003e or \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/spicy-mayo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003espicy mayo\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/tzatziki/?tp_image_id=121890\" data-pin-title=\"Tzatziki\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/20