4/01/tzatziki-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-for-making\"\u003eTips for Making\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eI will usually peel the skin (or most of the skin) from the cucumber before grating and straining. This isn’t totally necessary but I think it results in less chewy bits in the tzatziki. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eYou can add the cucumber juice to a big glass of water for a refreshing treat—no need to waste it, it’s delicious!\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIf I am serving this as a dip, I will usually drizzle a little more oil on top before serving for a pretty presentation. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIf you don’t have vinegar on hand, fresh squeezed lemon juice works great. \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/tzatziki/?tp_image_id=121893\" data-pin-title=\"Tzatziki\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/how-to-make-tzatziki.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-serving-suggestions\"\u003eServing Suggestions\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTzatziki can be used as a dip, sauce or spread—similar to \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/hummus/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ehummus\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse a dip with fresh cut vegetables or warm pita bread or \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/homemade-whole-wheat-flatbread/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eflatbread\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIt pairs nicely with a Greek salad, tabbouleh and a spread of olives.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eSpread on a \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/everything-bagels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ebagel\u003c/a\u003e with lox or avocado on top.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eSpread on a sandwich, wrap or hamburger—especially if it features other Mediterranean or Middle Eastern flavors. \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/tzatziki/?tp_image_id=121894\" data-pin-title=\"Tzatziki\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/tzatziki-recipe.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-121896\" data-recipe-id=\"121896\" data-servings=\"6\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"acf-helper-block_ccbe6046e20377688307d9a8b1994889\"\u003e\n\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGet our FREE recipe guide with our \u003cem\u003emost popular\u003c/em\u003e recipes of all time!\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"#popup-1\" data-lity=\"\"\u003eGet the Guide\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003csection\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIngredients\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"121896\" data-servings=\"6\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecucumber\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecloves\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003egarlic\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003evinegar\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eolive oil\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003edill\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eplain Greek yogurt\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003esalt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ch3\u003eInstructions\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"121896\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-121896-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGrate the cucumber. Remove excess cucumber juice by squeezing in cheesecloth or paper towels.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-121896-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMince the garlic.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-121896-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFinely chop the dill.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-121896-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIn a mixing bowl, stir together the yogurt, strained cucumber, garlic, vinegar, olive oil and dill. Taste and add salt and pepper as you feel needed.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-121896-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eRefrigerate for at least 30 minutes and up to three days. The flavors will intensify some as the dip is stored.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis recipe makes about 2 1/2 cups of tzatziki dip, which I am listing as 6 servings in the recipe card for nutrition facts purposes. But it may be more or less servings depending what you are using it for. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI will usually peel the skin (or most of the skin) from the cucumber before grating and straining. This isn’t totally necessary but I think it results in less chewy bits in the tzatziki.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIf I am serving this as a dip, I will usually drizzle a little more oil on top before serving for a pretty presentation.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSometimes, I will add a little fresh mint as well, but it’s optional.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdetails\u003e\n\n    \u003csummary\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cp\u003eNutrition Facts\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTzatziki\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAmount per Serving\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e% Daily Value*\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Percent Daily Values are based on a 2000 calorie diet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eNotice: Nutrition is auto-calculated, using Spoonacular, for your convenience. Where relevant, we recommend using your own nutrition calculations.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/details\u003e\n\n\n\t\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003c/main\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
